conbody.p:
The array_insert function inserts a value into a specific position in an
      array and returns the new array.
      array array_insert( array-name, position, value)SELECT ARRAY_INSERT(schedule, 2, "jsmith")[2]  
  FROM `travel-sample` 
  WHERE type = "route"  
  LIMIT 1;
       {
